headline.main: YIELD, 5 TO 4, FIRST AT TROPICAL PARK; Outruns Cosmonaut by Two Lengths--Ussery Scores With Three Mounts Helicopter Falters on Turn Switch On 8-5 Favorite

results.snippet: CORAL GABLES, Fla., Jan. 4 (AP)--Hasty House Farms' Yield, with Sidney Lejeune in the saddle, raced to expectations when he captured the seventh and best race on the drab program today at Tropical Park.

headline.main: TROPIC KING WINS FLORIDA FEATURE; My Night Out Runs Fourth in Field of 12, Ending Victory String at 5

results.snippet: CORAL GABLES, Fla., Jan. 8 (AP)--The winning streak of My Night Out was snapped at Tropical Park today. The heavily-backed choice finished a soundly beaten fourth as the Fairway Farm's Tropic King won the featured seventh race.
